| Aspect      | writeFile                                 | appendFile                                     |
| ----------- | ----------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------- |
| Behavior    | Overwrites/replaces all content linkedin​ | Adds to end, keeps existing geeksforgeeks​     |
| Use Case    | Config files, fresh reports linkedin​     | Logs, audit trails linkedin​                   |
| File Exists | Truncates and rewrites hayageek​          | Appends without altering geeksforgeeks​        |
| API Style   | fs.writeFile('file.txt', data) hayageek​  | fs.appendFile('file.txt', data) geeksforgeeks​ |
